Title: REST API: allow effective host attributes to be queries
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: core
Date: 1610375536
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

The host_config GET REST API endpoint now accepts an "effective_attributes" query, parameter. When
this parameter is set, all the parameters of the host and all it's parent folders are combined and
returned. The default behavior is to only return the host's attributes.
